The Japanese. In the caves.

49:18.205 --> 49:20.040
- Go on.
- Okinawa.

49:20.082 --> 49:22.084
They didn't believe the war was over.

49:22.126 --> 49:24.170
That's right. So, now we have
a guy who doesn't believe...

49:24.211 --> 49:26.338
No, no. We have an American serviceman.

49:26.380 --> 49:29.425
