49:41.228 --> 49:42.354
- Fruitcake.
- There you go.

49:42.396 --> 49:44.648
All right. Let's work. Ok?

49:44.690 --> 49:46.901
We got a guy who's left behind, so...

49:46.942 --> 49:49.528
This is terrific. This
