49:57.828 --> 49:59.038
- Shoe.
- Old shoe?

49:59.079 --> 50:02.208
It's just instinct.

50:02.249 --> 50:04.418
I want you to give me the Pentagon...

50:04.460 --> 50:08.130
...a list of people in all
military special programs.

50:08.172 --> 50:11.300
"Left behind like an
old shoe." That is good.

50:11.342 --> 50:15.346
I want to talk to Johnny.

50:17.097 --> 50:18.349
Yeah... What is it?

50:18.390 --> 50:21.227
The war is over. Ok?

