Now, we're going to need a new song.

50:23.604 --> 50:26.899
I think, it should be a song
about a shoe, a shiny shoe...

50:26.941 --> 50:28.859
...a black patent shoe...

50:28.901 --> 50:30.736
...a good old shoe.

50:30.778 --> 50:33.530
I was just on my way to get drunk.

50:33.572 --> 50:37.618
Yes, you get drunk, John. But I need
a new song, ok? A good old shoe song.

50:37.660 --> 50:40.412
It should be a ballad of loss and...

50:40.454 --> 50:42.122
- You wanna to help me?
- Redemption.

50:42.164 --> 50:45.793
Loss and redemption is very very good.

50:45.834 --> 50:48.963
Shit. What key do you want it in?

50:49.004 --> 50:51.632
I don't know keys.

50:51.674 --> 50:55.761
I got a lot of people here are
depressed because the war just ended.

50:55.803 --> 50:57.638
Please give me a new song.

50:57.680 --> 50:59.598
All right. I got him on the phone.

50:59.640 --> 51:01.976
- King? - Yeah.
- Pentagon.

51:02.017 --> 51:03.227
Take it.

51:03.269 --> 51:07.106
I need a list of military
special programs.

51:07.147 --> 51:09.316
Bottom of the ninth. All right?

51:09.358 --> 51:12.319
They don't know who
