53:04.098 --> 53:08.894
I see where you're going with this.

53:11.271 --> 53:13.440
Stand up straight and tall...

53:13.482 --> 53:15.692
...the way he taught you to.

53:15.734 --> 53:18.821
I'll write a speech.

53:18.862 --> 53:20.906
I'll help you with the speech.

53:20.948 --> 53:26.036
The president reveals
that William Schumann...

53:26.078 --> 53:29.415
...was trapped behind enemy lines.

53:29.456 --> 53:31.583
This is good.

53:31.625 --> 53:33.293
Heartfelt.

53:33.335 --> 53:35.921
- Touching.
- Touching.

53:35.963 --> 53:38.340
People will weep.

53:38.382 --> 53:42.302
Soul of a good ol' shoe.

53:43.679 --> 53:45.931
He might even get to heaven...

53:45.973 --> 53:50.853
...on the soul of his good ol' shoe.

