54:41.069 --> 54:43.530
...but, Lord willing,
eight days from now...

54:43.572 --> 54:46.241
...I'm gonna be taking
you into the second term.

54:46.283 --> 54:47.659
Wait till you hear the speech tonight.

54:47.701 --> 54:49.661
The 303 speech. Great.

54:49.703 --> 54:51.538
Where's that Fad King by the way?

54:51.580 --> 54:52.498
I'll get him.

54:52.539 --> 54:54.041
Could we go now please people?

54:54.082 --> 54:56.460
A good plan today is better
than a perfect plan tomorrow.

54:56.502 --> 54:59.171
Conrad, how are they doing
on Sergeant Schumann?

54:59.213 --> 55:00.714
They're working on him,
they're finding him.

55:00.756 --> 55:02.341
Good. It's working.

55:02.382 --> 55:04.927
It's all happening people.
It's taking place around us.

55:04.968 --> 55:08.722
People, it is in the works.
It is being addressed.

55:08.764 --> 55:10.057
We are being proactive.

55:10.098 --> 55:13.227
We are going out tonight with
what may be the finest example...

55:13.268 --> 55:15.979
Get me an update on
the army, the Pentagon.

55:16.021 --> 55:17.523
Get this guy Schumann. Put him on hold.

55:17.564 --> 55:18.941
Have him standing by.

55:18.982 --> 55:23.237
People I gotta tell you, I
see a lot of glum faces now.

55:23.278 --> 55:24.905
