55:24.947 --> 55:28.158
This is politics at its finest.

55:28.200 --> 55:30.410
This is where the rubber meets the road.

55:30.452 --> 55:33.413
Now I'm gonna tell that we've
got a leader going out tonight...

55:33.455 --> 55:35.123
