56:50.490 --> 56:54.119
I want you to get me 30 secretaries
and put them in an office now.

56:54.161 --> 56:56.038
Would you do that? You just
tell him I'm coming up.

56:56.079 --> 56:59.041
I need to see the president
and five minutes of this time.

56:59.082 --> 57:01.084
Speech is corny. Know
what this reminds me of?

57:01.126 --> 57:04.046
