needs a little bit a "umph".

57:40.207 --> 57:43.251
Bear with me.

57:45.671 --> 57:49.091
Thank you so much.

57:59.601 --> 58:01.770
That was so moving.

58:01.812 --> 58:03.188
Thank you so much.

58:03.230 --> 58:06.024
Thank you.

58:10.529 --> 58:13.949
You konow, Connie? I felt
very much at home in there.

58:13.990 --> 58:15.534
