58:15.575 --> 58:17.160
I could have gone this way.

58:17.202 --> 58:19.204
It's all a change in wardrobe.

58:19.246 --> 58:21.206
So, what do you think? Was it too much?

58:21.248 --> 58:24.334
I'll tell you, Stanley.

58:24.376 --> 58:26.545
- You did it.
- Yeah.

58:26.586 --> 58:27.921
You did it. You jumped in there...

58:27.963 --> 58:29.840
...and saved the thing when
the thing needed saving.

58:29.881 --> 58:31.842
You don't think it was too much?

58:31.883 --> 58:33.760
Personally?

58:33.802 --> 58:35.053
Maybe it was.

58:35.095 --> 58:38.223
Of course the president doesn't
have to say it that way, Connie.

58:38.265 --> 58:40.225
It's like Plato once said.

58:40.267 --> 58:42.728
It doesn't matter how the fuck you
get there as long as you get there.

58:42.769 --> 58:44.229
He said that?

58:44.271 --> 58:46.523
Connie, what is it exactly
you do for the president?

58:46.565 --> 58:49.568
