Whatever.

01:09:32.960 --> 01:09:34.545
Everybody's gotta learn.

01:09:34.587 --> 01:09:37.631
Any business.

01:09:38.091 --> 01:09:39.300
You take the fruit of 40 years...

01:09:39.341 --> 01:09:41.636
...hard lessons, mistakes,
and you call it wisdom.

01:09:41.676 --> 01:09:42.970
That's the truth.

01:09:43.011 --> 01:09:45.680
End of the day, just when
you know something...

01:09:45.723 --> 01:09:47.225
...time to go home.

01:09:47.265 --> 01:09:49.394
Stanley, you got decades in you now.

01:09:49.435 --> 01:09:51.437
You got decades left in you.

01:09:51.479 --> 01:09:54.440
Yeah, but...

01:09:54.774 --> 01:09:57.735
What could I do to top this?

01:09:57.777 --> 01:10:01.072
♪ The 37th Psalm.

01:10:01.656 --> 01:10:06.411
♪ I'll do the same in His great name...

01:10:06.452 --> 01:10:09.247
♪ ...if you have courage, Mom.

