- She cried.
- Really?

01:10:16.671 --> 01:10:19.132
- She cried real.
- It looks it.

01:10:19.173 --> 01:10:21.551
♪ Pray for me...

01:10:21.592 --> 01:10:23.928
♪ ...and the USA.

